astrophotography-toolkit
========

This is a program/library that contains some implementations of
photography techniques and some whatever stuff being developed as a
past-time project of a full time university student, use at your own
discretion.

======== Prerequisites:

python >= 3.10

refer to REQUIREMENTS for python dependencies

======== Setup:

To setup the project start by creating a virtual environment using
python's venv:

    python -m venv <venv-name>

Then:

    source <venv-name>/bin/activate

Install the dependencies with `pip install -r REQUIREMENTS` and run the
main script with `python -m src.main`

